										{
											"type": "code"
										}
									],
									"text": "Hero ↓  Growth Snapshot (your current cards) ↓  Services ✅ ↓  Featured Results / Case Studies ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐ ↓  Why Choose Apex ↓  Our Process ↓  Marketing Stats ↓  Website & App Development ↓  Testimonials ↓  FAQ ↓  CTA ↓  Footer"
