							"content": [
								{
									"type": "text",
									"marks": [
										{
											"type": "code"
										}
									],
									"text": "✓ Strategy First  Every campaign begins with research, competitor analysis and customer intent.  --------------------------  ✓ Transparent Reporting  Know exactly where every rupee goes.  --------------------------  ✓ AI Automation  Follow-ups. Lead scoring. CRM integrations.  --------------------------  ✓ Fast Execution  Launch campaigns within days, not weeks.  --------------------------  ✓ Dedicated Support  One point of contact. Always available."
